speaker: user
message: How can I fix an issue with reaching the VPN server, Access Server?

welcome_message:
Hello! I'm agent aibot-openvpn.
I'm here to answer any questions you have, or maybe you'd rather choose a question others are asking me?
[more about me >](action/profile)
speaker: assistant
message:
To fix an issue with reaching the VPN server, Access Server, you can try the following troubleshooting steps:

1. Verify that the VPN server address resolves correctly by using a custom hostname or DNS record that resolves to the correct public IP address. You can use an online DNS checker tool to verify the status of the DNS record. [Troubleshooting An OpenVPN Access Server Failure - Verify that the VPN server address resolves correctly](https://openvpn.net/vpn-server-resources/restoring-a-failed-access-server-to-normal-function/)

2. Check if you can reach the Access Server web interface by accessing it directly using the server's public IP address in your web browser. This can help identify if there are any issues with DNS records. [Troubleshooting An OpenVPN Access Server Failure - Verify that the server can be reached by its IP address](https://openvpn.net/vpn-server-resources/restoring-a-failed-access-server-to-normal-function/)

3. Confirm that the server is still on the same IP address. If the server's IP address has changed, update the DNS record or the Hostname/IP address setting in the Admin Web UI of the Access Server. Reprovision all installed VPN clients to use the correct new address. [Troubleshooting An OpenVPN Access Server Failure - Verify that your server is still on the same IP address](https://openvpn.net/vpn-server-resources/restoring-a-failed-access-server-to-normal-function/)

4. If the above steps don't resolve the issue, verify if the server is alive by pinging its IP address. If there is no response, it indicates that the server or its network connection may be down. [Troubleshooting An OpenVPN Access Server Failure - Confirm that the server is alive](https://openvpn.net/vpn-server-resources/restoring-a-failed-access-server-to-normal-function/)

5. Try accessing the server via SSH to perform maintenance tasks. If you can establish an SSH connection, it indicates that the server is up and running. Make sure to have the necessary credentials/keys to log in. [Troubleshooting An OpenVPN Access Server Failure - Try to access the server via SSH](https://openvpn.net/vpn-server-resources/restoring-a-failed-access-server-to-normal-function/)

If the issue persists after trying these troubleshooting steps, it is recommended to contact the support team for further assistance. [Troubleshooting An OpenVPN Access Server Failure](https://openvpn.net/vpn-server-resources/restoring-a-failed-access-server-to-normal-function/)

message: How can I fix issues with my VPN server and a persistent connection?

welcome_message:
Hello! I'm agent aibot-openvpn.
I'm here to answer any questions you have, or maybe you'd rather choose a question others are asking me?
[more about me >](action/profile)
speaker: assistant
message:
To fix issues with your VPN server and a persistent connection, you can try the following steps:

1. Verify that the VPN server address resolves correctly: Use a custom hostname that resolves to the public IP address of your Access Server through a DNS record. Ensure that the DNS record resolves to the correct IP address. You can use an online DNS checker tool to verify the status of the DNS record. [More details](https://openvpn.net/vpn-server-resources/restoring-a-failed-access-server-to-normal-function/)

2. Verify that the server can be reached by its IP address: Access the OpenVPN Access Server web interface directly in your web browser using the server's public IP address. For example, if the server's IP address is 123.45.67.89, try accessing it at https://123.45.67.89. [More details](https://openvpn.net/vpn-server-resources/restoring-a-failed-access-server-to-normal-function/)

3. Verify that your server is still on the same IP address: Check if the public IP address of your Access Server has changed. If it has, update the DNS record or the Hostname/IP address setting in the Admin Web UI of the Access Server. Reprovision all installed VPN clients to use the correct new address. [More details](https://openvpn.net/vpn-server-resources/restoring-a-failed-access-server-to-normal-function/)

If the issue persists after trying these steps, consider updating your OS and the Access Server. If the problem continues, contact the support team for further assistance. [More details](https://openvpn.net/vpn-server-resources/restoring-a-failed-access-server-to-normal-function/)

message: How do I uninstall Access Server?

welcome_message:
Hello! I'm agent aibot-openvpn.
I'm here to answer any questions you have, or maybe you'd rather choose a question others are asking me?
[more about me >](action/profile)
speaker: assistant
message:
To uninstall Access Server, you can follow the steps below:

1. Connect to your server's terminal.
2. Run the following command to remove the Access Server package:

```
sudo apt-get remove openvpnas
```

3. After the package is removed, you can also remove any remaining configuration files by running the following command:

```
sudo rm -rf /usr/local/openvpn_as
```

Please note that uninstalling Access Server will remove the software from your server, but it will not deactivate any subscription or license associated with it. If you want to deactivate your subscription or license, you will need to do so separately through the Access Server licensing portal on the OpenVPN website.

For more information, you can refer to the [Configuration Database Management And Backups](https://openvpn.net/vpn-server-resources/configuration-database-management-and-backups/) documentation.

message: How can I access folders and files through the VPN?

welcome_message:
Hello! I'm agent aibot-openvpn.
I'm here to answer any questions you have, or maybe you'd rather choose a question others are asking me?
[more about me >](action/profile)
speaker: assistant
message:
To access folders and files through the VPN, you can follow these steps:

Step 1: Set up Access Server routing
- Sign in to the Admin Web UI.
- Click Configuration > VPN Settings.
- Under Routing, add the IP address of the remote server to "Specify the private subnets to which all clients should be given access."
- Click Save Settings and Update running server.

Step 2: Access the files from your device
- Launch the OpenVPN Connect app on your device.
- Connect to the Access Server.
- Open the file explorer on your device.
- In the address bar, type the local IP address of the remote server in the format: `\\<Remote Windows Server IP>`.
- Hit Enter.
- You will be prompted for a username and password for the remote server.
- Enter the credentials and access the shared folders and files.

Please note that these steps assume you have Access Server installed, OpenVPN Connect app installed on your device, and the necessary permissions to access the remote server. For more details, you can refer to the [Access Server: Access Windows shared folders/files over OpenVPN (use case)](https://support.openvpn.com/hc/en-us/articles/21823624381723-Access-Server-Access-Windows-shared-folders-files-over-OpenVPN-use-case) article in the OpenVPN Support Center.

[Access Server: Access Windows shared folders/files over OpenVPN (use case)](https://support.openvpn.com/hc/en-us/articles/21823624381723-Access-Server-Access-Windows-shared-folders-files-over-OpenVPN-use-case)

message: How can I fix the error when trying to renew the certificate using certbot?

welcome_message:
Hello! I'm agent aibot-openvpn.
I'm here to answer any questions you have, or maybe you'd rather choose a question others are asking me?
[more about me >](action/profile)
speaker: assistant
message:
If you encountered an error while trying to renew the SSL certificate using certbot, you can follow these steps to troubleshoot and resolve the issue:

1. Confirm the error by reviewing the log for error messages similar to those listed above:
   ```
   cat /var/log/letsencrypt/letsencrypt.log
   ```

2. Check if port 80 is used for any application on your Access Server host:
   ```
   netstat -anlp|grep ":80"
   ```

3. Troubleshoot using TCP dump:
   - Install the tcpdump tool from repositories:
     - For Ubuntu/Debian OS: `apt install tcpdump`
     - For CentOS/RHEL: `yum install tcpdump`
   - Capture packets sent to port 80:
     ```
     tcpdump -ni any port 80
     ```

4. Ensure that port 80 is really open by launching a simple HTTP server on the Access Server host and then browsing it:
   ```
   mkdir /tmp/tempweb/
   echo "Port 80 is open" > /tmp/tempweb/index.html
   cd /tmp/tempweb/
   sudo python3 -m http.server 80
   ```
   Then go to `` in your browser. If everything is OK, you should be able to see the text "Port 80 is open".

For more details and troubleshooting steps, you can refer to the [Access server: Certbot error port 80](https://support.openvpn.com/hc/en-us/articles/12183959644443-Access-server-Certbot-error-port-80) documentation.

[Access server: Certbot error port 80 - OpenVPN Support Center](https://support.openvpn.com/hc/en-us/articles/12183959644443-Access-server-Certbot-error-port-80)

message: What do I do about TLS compatibility?

welcome_message:
Hello! I'm agent aibot-openvpn.
I'm here to answer any questions you have, or maybe you'd rather choose a question others are asking me?
[more about me >](action/profile)
speaker: assistant
message:
To ensure TLS compatibility for your OpenVPN setup, you can configure the TLS control channel security setting in the Admin Web UI under Configuration > Advanced VPN. OpenVPN Access Server version 2.9 and newer supports TLS Crypt v2 connection profiles, even if the TLS control channel security level is set to TLS Auth or TLS Crypt. It is recommended to keep TLS control channel security enabled for added security. 

For more information, you can refer to the OpenVPN Access Server documentation on TLS Control Channel Security: [TLS Control Channel Security in OpenVPN Access Server](https://openvpn.net/vpn-server-resources/tls-control-channel-security-in-openvpn-access-server/)

message: How can I backup and restore Access Server?

welcome_message:
Hello! I'm agent aibot-openvpn.
I'm here to answer any questions you have, or maybe you'd rather choose a question others are asking me?
[more about me >](action/profile)
speaker: assistant
message:
To backup and restore Access Server, you can follow these steps:

1. Use the provided commands with root privileges to make a backup of the configuration files on your existing server:
   ```
   which apt > /dev/null 2>&1 && apt -y install sqlite3
   which yum > /dev/null 2>&1 && yum -y install sqlite
   cd /usr/local/openvpn_as/etc/db
   [ -e config.db ]&&sqlite3 config.db .dump>../../config.db.bak
   [ -e certs.db ]&&sqlite3 certs.db .dump>../../certs.db.bak
   [ -e userprop.db ]&&sqlite3 userprop.db .dump>../../userprop.db.bak
   [ -e log.db ]&&sqlite3 log.db .dump>../../log.db.bak
   [ -e config_local.db ]&&sqlite3 config_local.db .dump>../../config_local.db.bak
   [ -e cluster.db ]&&sqlite3 cluster.db .dump>../../cluster.db.bak
   [ -e clusterdb.db ]&&sqlite3 clusterdb.db .dump>../../clusterdb.db.bak
   [ -e notification.db ]&&sqlite3 notification.db .dump>../../notification.db.bak
   cp ../as.conf ../../as.conf.bak
   ```

2. The resulting backup files will be stored in `/usr/local/openvpn_as/` with the `.bak` extension.

3. Set up a new Access Server instance.

4. Restore the backup files on the new server by following the steps outlined in the documentation.

Please note that the provided commands are for backing up the configuration files and databases. Other considerations, such as IP address changes and DNS record updates, may also be necessary. For more detailed instructions and additional information, you can refer to the [documentation on migrating an Access Server installation](https://openvpn.net/vpn-server-resources/migrating-an-access-server-installation/).

Documentation: [Migrating An Access Server Installation](https://openvpn.net/vpn-server-resources/migrating-an-access-server-installation/)

Hello! I'm agent aibot-openvpn.
I'm here to answer any questions you have, or maybe you'd rather choose a question others are asking me?
[more about me >](action/profile)
speaker: assistant
message:
Connection profiles refer to the .ovpn text files that contain the directives, parameters, and certificates required to establish a client-server VPN connection. These profiles include information such as server addresses, ports, peer identity verification, TLS control channel security, and other settings. They are used to configure and establish VPN connections with OpenVPN Connect. 

[Connection Profiles Documentation](https://openvpn.net/connect-docs/connection-profiles.html)

   - Windows: [Import a connection profile from file](connect-for-windows.html)

Please note that the specific download link may vary depending on your use case and the type of connection profile you need.

message: How can a knowledge base help improve customer experience?

welcome_message:
Hello! I'm agent d-1-5-24.
I'm here to answer any questions you have, or maybe you'd rather choose a question others are asking me?
[more about me >](action/profile)
speaker: assistant
message:
A knowledge base can help improve customer experience in several ways:

1. **Easy access to information**: Customers can easily access the knowledge base to find answers to their questions without having to reach out to the support team or wait for a response.

2. **Logical organization**: By structuring the knowledge base in a logical way with categories and collections, customers can quickly find the information they need. For example, having a search feature, popular searches section, and navigation menu for browsing articles can enhance the customer experience.

3. **Excellent search feature**: The knowledge base should have a search feature that delivers fast and accurate results, even handling misspellings and common typing errors. This allows customers to quickly find the information they're looking for.

4. **Clear and concise content**: Writing clear, concise, and easily digestible content in the knowledge base ensures that customers can easily understand and find the answers they need.

5. **Data-driven decisions**: Analyzing metrics such as page views, bounce rates, and time on page can help optimize the knowledge base and improve user flows, making it easier for customers to access the content they need.

6. **SEO optimization**: Applying SEO best practices to the knowledge base can help customers find the information they're looking for, whether they are browsing the knowledge base or searching on search engines like Google.

Overall, a well-designed and well-maintained knowledge base can provide customers with the information they need at the exact moment they need it, leading to a better customer experience.

The main challenges faced by Facility Management in the Banking & Insurance industry include:

- Lack of monitoring, financial, and operational reporting
- Insufficient resources
- Poor follow-up and control on expenses
- Mismatch of information
- Poor decision-making management
- Need for reporting and process improvement

message: What are the characteristics common to most unicorns?

welcome_message:
Hello! I'm agent unicorn-spotter-9125.
I'm here to answer any questions you have, or maybe you'd rather choose a question others are asking me?
[more about me >](action/profile)
speaker: assistant
message:
Most unicorns, regardless of the industry or sector, tend to have the following characteristics:

1. Disruptive innovation: Unicorns have a game-changing product or service that can disrupt the industry's status quo and revolutionize the way it operates.

2. First mover advantage: Many unicorn start-ups are the first to introduce a product or service to the market, capitalizing on newly created demand and establishing their brands among consumers.

3. B2C focused: About 60% of unicorn start-ups sell directly to consumers. This allows them to cultivate a strong consumer base and brand, which are essential for driving growth.

4. Tech savvy and efficient: Many unicorns emerge from a tech-related field. They either introduce new technologies or adopt new tech to create viable products that can be rapidly adjusted to market demand.

5. Growth driven: A start-up must have an ambitious growth strategy to attract the funding level that elevates it to unicorn status.

These characteristics set unicorns apart from most start-ups and contribute to their potential for substantial growth and outsize returns.

message: What skills and expertise are required to properly implement, configure, and manage a SIEM solution?

welcome_message: Hello! I'm the cybersecurity-brainiac.  I am trained to provide information on a wide range of infosec subjects from reading all 12 years of Cyber Defense Magazine (16,500+ pages of content). Sponsored this month by ![UnknownCyber](https://www.cyberdefensemagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unknowncyber.jpg) [UnknownCyber](https://www.unknowncyber.com/), the market leader of zero day malware detection.
speaker: assistant
message:
The skills and expertise required to properly implement, configure, and manage a SIEM solution include:

1. Threat Intelligence: The value of a SIEM solution depends heavily on the threat intelligence feeds it uses. Security experts with knowledge of threat intelligence are needed to effectively utilize these feeds.

2. Log Management: SIEM systems require expertise in log management to collect, store, and analyze logs from various sources. This involves understanding different log formats, data normalization, and log retention policies.

3. Threat Detection: Security experts with knowledge of threat detection techniques are essential to configure the SIEM solution to identify and alert on potential security incidents. This includes creating correlation rules, defining thresholds, and analyzing patterns.

4. Forensic Analysis: In the event of a security incident, forensic analysis is necessary to investigate and understand the scope and impact of the incident. Security experts with expertise in forensic analysis can perform detailed investigations and provide insights for remediation.

It is important to note that implementing and managing a SIEM solution requires significant effort and expertise. Organizations should have security professionals with these skills or consider partnering with external experts to ensure the effective implementation and management of the SIEM solution.

speaker: assistant
message: Trained, experienced analysts play a crucial role in border security. They are responsible for investigating crimes at or across borders. message: What skills and expertise are required to properly implement, configure, and manage a SIEM solution?

welcome_message: Hello! I'm the cybersecurity-brainiac.  I am trained to provide information on a wide range of infosec subjects from reading all 12 years of Cyber Defense Magazine (16,500+ pages of content). Sponsored this month by ![UnknownCyber](https://www.cyberdefensemagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unknowncyber.jpg) [UnknownCyber](https://www.unknowncyber.com/), the market leader of zero day malware detection.
speaker: assistant
message:
The skills and expertise required to properly implement, configure, and manage a SIEM solution include:

1. Threat Intelligence: The value of a SIEM solution depends heavily on the threat intelligence feeds it uses. Security experts with knowledge of threat intelligence are needed to effectively utilize these feeds.

2. Log Management: SIEM systems require expertise in log management to collect, store, and analyze logs from various sources. This involves understanding different log formats, data normalization, and log retention policies.

3. Threat Detection: Security experts with knowledge of threat detection techniques are essential to configure the SIEM solution to identify and alert on potential security incidents. This includes creating correlation rules, defining thresholds, and analyzing patterns.

4. Forensic Analysis: In the event of a security incident, forensic analysis is crucial to investigate and understand the scope and impact of the incident. Security experts skilled in forensic analysis can perform detailed investigations and provide insights for remediation.

It is important to note that implementing, configuring, and managing a SIEM solution is complex and challenging. It requires a combination of technical skills, domain knowledge, and experience in cybersecurity.

speaker: assistant
message:
The basic background check package from NannyVerify.com has two components:

Background checks are provided by a third party, National Crime Search, Inc., an Arkansas-based corporation with a national background screening network. We offer background checks on US citizens, permanent residents and non-citizens possessing a valid Social Security Number (B, H and G visa holders for example), and Canadian citizens and permanent residents with valid Social Insurance Numbers (SIN).

At a minimum, all names and all addresses that were found by the SSN trace should have in-court county level records checked. Criminal records are only found when BOTH the name searched and the DOB match exactly.

It is very common for the more mature candidates to have the possibility of records under different names as a result of marriage and/or divorce. Families often learn information in the basic check that causes them to expand the initial search. Items may be added for up to 30 days beyond the initial search.

We recommend two ‘broad net’ tools that can help a family expand their screenings without spending a fortune. These are the National Sex Offenders Registry search and the the National Criminal Records Locator. These searches are strongly encouraged.

Driving records are very important, and they reveal more than just how well the nanny or senior caregiver drives.

A driving record can speak to the candidate’s judgment, attention to detail, and conformity to rules. DUI’s and speeding tickets will generally give a family pause.

Civil Court Records Searches are available as an optional add-on to the criminal records search. These can take several additional days to complete.

Please see [our resource dedicated to this ).

*What specific information are you looking to gather about the candidate's experience and criminal record?*

message:
The Taxpayer Advocate Service (TAS) can help if your problem is causing financial difficulties for you, your family, or your business, or if you face an immediate threat of adverse action due to unpaid taxes. If you think TAS might be able to help you, you can call your local advocate or the toll-free number at 1-877-777-4778. Deaf and hard of hearing individuals who have access to TDD/TTY equipment can call 1-800-829-4059. TAS also handles large-scale or systemic problems that affect many taxpayers. If you know of one of these broad issues, you can report it through the Systemic Advocacy Management System at [www.irs.gov/advocate](http://www.irs.gov/uac/Taxpayer-Advocate-Service-6).

To determine if you need to pay employment taxes, you should consider the following criteria:

- Paying cash wages of $1,800 or more in 2013 to any one household employee.
- Paying total cash wages of $1,000 or more in any calendar quarter of 2012 or 2013 to household employees.

If you meet these criteria, you will need to withhold and pay social security and Medicare taxes, as well as federal unemployment tax. You may also owe state unemployment tax. For further assistance, you can contact the IRS with your tax questions at 1-800-829-1040 or 1-800-829-4933.

*Have you already determined if you meet the criteria for paying employment taxes? How can I assist you further with your tax-related questions?*

message: DMARC stands for Domain-based Message Authentication, Reporting, and Conformance. It is a framework for email authentication that helps prevent email spoofing and phishing attacks. DMARC allows businesses to gain control over their email ecosystem, reduce the risk of unauthorized use of their domain, and ensure compliance with industry regulations. By implementing DMARC, businesses can either quarantine or reject suspicious emails, protecting their domain and their recipients from cyber threats.

welcome_message:

I'm here to answer any questions you have, or maybe you'd rather choose a question others are asking me?
[more about me >](action/profile)
speaker: assistant
message: Unity offers two forms of lighting: real-time lighting and pre-rendered lighting. Real-time lighting recalculates the lighting constantly to maintain coherence in the scene when objects or lights move. It can be computationally expensive and may cause performance issues, especially on mobile devices. Pre-rendered lighting, on the other hand, provides higher quality lighting and is recommended for static scenes. It involves pre-rendering the lighting with shadows for each object in the scene.

- Deluxe Euro 2 ST, 2/3 ST Deluxe, Dart, Hi 5: NZ$76.00
- Euro 2 ST, Ranger, Cruise, Kiwi 6, 7 Berths: NZ$82.00

message:
According to the Terms and Conditions of Kiwi Campers, there are road restrictions for driving the vehicle in New Zealand. The following roads are prohibited under all circumstances:

- Ninety Mile Beach – Northland
- North of Colville Township – Coromandel Peninsula
- Tapu-Coroglen Road – Coromandel Peninsula
- Skippers Canyon Road – Queenstown
- Ball Hutt Road – Mt. Cook
- All ski field’s access roads in both the North and South Islands from 1 June to 31 October
- Any beach or unformed/gravel roads in New Zealand, except for recognized campground access roads or road works.

Kiwi Campers also reserves the right to restrict vehicle movements in certain areas due to adverse road or weather conditions. It's important to note that if these road restrictions are breached, all insurances will become null and void, and the hirer will be liable for the full cost of any damages incurred.

message:
The cancellation policies for Kiwi Campers are as follows:

- 20 – 28 days: 20% of rental is retained by Kiwi Campers
- 10 – 19 days: 60% of rental is retained by Kiwi Campers
- 0 – 9 days: 100% of rental is retained by Kiwi Campers
- Cancelled on the day or No Show: 100% of rental is retained by Kiwi Campers

Please note that if a vehicle is picked up late or returned early, there is no refund available. Additionally, if an amendment is made to the rental dates within 28 days of collection and the length of hire is decreased, no refund will be made. A relocation fee may apply if the collection or return location is amended within 28 days of vehicle pick-up or if notification occurs during the hire.

[more about me >](action/profile)
speaker: assistant
message: During the Japanese occupation (1895-1945), Taiwan's industrial structure was not focused on the future economic takeoff of Taiwan. Instead, it served as a service provider for Japan's industrialization. Taiwan was developed into Japan's agricultural supply base, with a focus on agricultural product processing industries such as sugar and camphor. However, relying solely on this foundation made industrialization not possible.

The Local Explorers platform has been used to develop several apps for different regions and industries. Some examples include:

1. Maryland Craft Beverages App: This app was commissioned by the Maryland's Distillers Guild, Wineries Association, and Brewers Association. It showcases the state's craft beverages, including spirits, wine, and regional culinary specialties.

2. Vermont Brewery Challenge App: This app was developed for the Vermont Brewers Association. It allows users to explore and discover breweries in Vermont.

3. Taste of Nova Scotia App: This app showcases the food, craft beverages, and related events in Nova Scotia, Canada.

These apps incentivize users to visit and support local producers and retailers by offering directions, lists of available items, information about special events and offers, and the opportunity to earn points towards prizes. message:
BIGVU offers several AI-powered tools to enhance your video creation process. Here are some of the must-know features of BIGVU:

1. AI Script Generator: BIGVU helps you create scripts 10x faster by generating multiple script options based on your business and talking points.

2. Teleprompter: BIGVU's teleprompter feature lets you view your script while recording, helping you speak confidently on camera. You can customize the speed and font size to match your natural pace.

3. Auto Captions: BIGVU automatically generates captions for your videos, making it easier for viewers to follow along. You can also use AI to highlight important words or phrases in the captions.

4. Video Styling: BIGVU provides editing tools to style and brand your videos. You can add backgrounds, music, picture overlays, cropping, and titling to give your videos a polished look.

5. AI Eye Contact: If you looked away from the camera during your recording, you can use BIGVU AI instead of retaking the video. The AI Eye Contact will make it appear like you are looking directly at your audience.

6. Social Media Scheduling: With one tap, you can schedule and post your video across all your social media channels.

These features make BIGVU a comprehensive video creation platform that helps you create professional and engaging videos easily.

I would be happy to answer any questions you may have.
speaker: assistant
message: The conversion of electrical energy into hydrogen gas happens in an electrolyser unit. This energy is used to separate the water molecule into hydrogen and oxygen. The oxygen is released directly into the atmosphere, while the hydrogen gas is purified and compressed. After compression, the hydrogen gas is stored on the H2Neo Ship for export. The hydrogen gas is now a source of stored energy. Compressed hydrogen is chosen as a method of storage and transportation because it provides the lowest levelized cost of delivered hydrogen compared to other methods such as liquefaction and ammonia.

speaker: assistant
message:
When selecting a material for casting, there are several factors that need to be considered. These factors include:

1. Mechanical Properties: The material should have the necessary strength, hardness, and toughness to withstand the intended application and operating conditions.

2. Chemical Compatibility: The material should be resistant to corrosion and chemical reactions that may occur in the casting environment.

3. Thermal Properties: The material should have good heat resistance and thermal conductivity to prevent deformation or failure under high temperatures.

4. Casting Process: The material should be suitable for the casting process being used, such as sand casting, investment casting, or die casting.

5. Cost: The cost of the material, including its availability and production costs, should be considered in relation to the budget and project requirements.

6. Design Requirements: The material should be able to meet the specific design requirements, such as dimensional accuracy, surface finish, and complexity of the casting.

7. Environmental Impact: Consideration should be given to the environmental impact of the material, such as its recyclability and sustainability.

By taking these factors into account, the appropriate material can be selected for a casting application.

speaker: assistant
message:
42CrMo is a steel grade that falls under the category of alloy steels. It is also known as ML42CrMo and is classified as a quenched and tempered steel for cold heading and cold extruding applications. It is specified in the GB/T 6478-2015 standard for steels used in cold heading and cold extruding processes. 

42CrMo offers similar performance to ML35CrMo steel, but it has higher strength, better hardenability, higher fatigue strength, and excellent resistance to multiple impacts. It is commonly used for manufacturing high-strength fasteners, such as hexagon flange bolts, hex head bolts, double-end bolts, and high-strength bolts with minimal head deformation. It is recommended for applications that require higher strength than ML35CrMo steel, with a temperature range of -65°C to +400°C.

For more detailed information, you can refer to the [GB/T 6478-2015 standard](https://www.caishuku.com/material/detail_412764.html).

message:
Risk-HR is an assessment tool designed to evaluate potential risks related to various aspects of an individual's behavior and attitudes in the workplace. It helps organizations make informed decisions during the hiring process or when assessing current employees. The assessment consists of different types of questions: general, semi-personal, and personal. 

The results of the assessment range from 0 to 100%. A normal range for a test taker is considered to be 0 to 60%. If an assessee receives an alert (61% or higher), it indicates a potential risk that should be further analyzed. There are two types of alerts: preemptive alerts (61% to 80%) and real alerts (81% to 100%).

The assessment covers various topics, such as drug use, alcohol consumption, organized crime, teamwork, loyalty to the company, and more. Each question and topic carries a different level of risk. The assessment can be conducted in short or long versions, depending on the specific needs of the organization.

It's important to note that Risk-HR does not pass judgment on the results of evaluations. However, in situations where there are potential risks identified, it is generally recommended to repeat the assessment in a controlled environment or view it as a potential attempt to defraud the organization.

[more about me >](action/profile)
speaker: assistant
message:
The key features of the Datwyler Smart Service Platform (SSP) are:

1. Service portal and rich data visualization: The platform provides a web-based portal with a modern user interface for managing and configuring your IoT environment. It offers various widgets for visualizing different types of data, such as telemetry, statistics, geolocation, and software updates.

2. Alerts, triggers, and notifications: The platform includes a rule engine that allows you to set up alerts when specific rules are breached. You can configure communication channels like email, Slack, SMS, and push notifications for receiving alerts and notifications.

3. Device management: The platform offers comprehensive device management and remote maintenance capabilities for IoT devices. This includes device onboarding and provisioning, configuration and control, software and firmware updates, monitoring and diagnostics, and troubleshooting features.

4. Data processing and reporting: The platform collects and stores diverse data from multiple IoT devices, allowing for further processing, analysis, and reporting. It supports the transformation of raw, unstructured data into well-structured time series data for analytics and visualization.

5. AI-based analytics: The platform includes an out-of-the-box predictive analytics engine that uses advanced AI and deep learning technologies for forecasting and anomaly detection in time series data.

These features provide organizations with greater visibility, control, and security over their critical IT and OT infrastructure worldwide.

The stadium has welcomed numerous legendary cricketers and has witnessed several historic cricketing moments, like Virender Sehwag's fantastic 319 against South Africa in 2008. Feel free to ask any further questions you may have about this spectacular cricket arena full of rich history.

message: What skills and expertise are required to properly implement, configure, and manage a SIEM solution?

welcome_message: Hello! I'm the cybersecurity-brainiac.  I am trained to provide information on a wide range of infosec subjects from reading all 12 years of Cyber Defense Magazine (16,500+ pages of content). Sponsored this month by ![UnknownCyber](https://www.cyberdefensemagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unknowncyber.jpg) [UnknownCyber](https://www.unknowncyber.com/), the market leader of zero day malware detection.
speaker: assistant
message:
The skills and expertise required to properly implement, configure, and manage a SIEM solution include:

1. Threat Intelligence: The value of a SIEM solution depends heavily on the threat intelligence feeds it uses. Security experts with knowledge of threat intelligence are needed to effectively utilize these feeds.

2. Log Management: SIEM systems require expertise in log management to collect, store, and analyze logs from various sources. This involves understanding different log formats, data normalization, and log retention policies.

3. Threat Detection: Security experts with knowledge of threat detection techniques are essential to configure the SIEM solution to identify and alert on potential security incidents. This includes creating correlation rules, defining thresholds, and analyzing patterns.

4. Forensic Analysis: In the event of a security incident, forensic analysis is necessary to investigate and understand the scope and impact of the incident. Security experts with expertise in forensic analysis can perform detailed investigations and provide insights for remediation.

It is important to note that implementing and managing a SIEM solution requires significant effort and expertise. Organizations should have security professionals with these skills or consider partnering with external experts to ensure the effective implementation and management of the SIEM solution.

message: What is the purpose of freezing the feature-extraction layers in transfer learning?

welcome_message:

speaker: assistant
message: In transfer learning, the purpose of freezing the feature-extraction layers is to keep the weights of these layers fixed and unchanged. By doing so, the previously-trained model's learned features can be preserved and utilized as a starting point for training on a new dataset. This allows the network to adapt and specialize to the new dataset without modifying the already learned representations in the feature-extraction layers.

speaker: assistant
message:
A literature review on determining Gleason grade based on deep learning methods reveals several studies that have explored the potential of deep neural networks in automating and enhancing the Gleason grading process for prostate cancer.

One study by Nagpal et al. [5] demonstrated the potential of deep neural network-based systems for Gleason grading of prostate carcinoma. They utilized a large dataset of annotated, digitized tissue sections to train and evaluate their AI model. Their work showcased the predictive capabilities of deep neural networks in accurately grading prostate cancer.

Another study by Arvaniti et al. [34] and Karimi et al. [32] highlighted the robust predictive capabilities of portable architectures like MobileNet for both cancer detection and fine classification in Gleason grading. These studies emphasized the importance of established and smaller deep neural network architectures in achieving accurate results.

Furthermore, custom CNN architectures specifically designed for Gleason grading, as shown in the work of Bhattacharjee et al. [35], Duran-Lopez et al. [36], and Silva-Rodriguez et al. [37], have also demonstrated promise in improving the accuracy of Gleason grading.

Overall, these studies have shown that deep learning methods, particularly deep neural networks, have the potential to streamline and enhance the Gleason grading process, reducing interobserver variability and improving diagnostic consistency. They provide valuable insights into the performance and architecture of deep learning models for Gleason grading, paving the way for further advancements in AI-assisted prostate cancer diagnosis.

To add a proxy using Connect, follow these steps:

1. Launch OpenVPN Connect.
2. Click or tap the menu icon.
3. Click "Proxies."
4. Click "Add."
5. Enter the details for your proxy, including the Proxy Friendly Name, Proxy Hostname or IP, Port, Username, Password, and whether to use basic authentication.
6. Click "Save."

You can now apply your proxy to a connection profile.

For more detailed instructions, you can refer to the [Create a proxy configuration](https://openvpn.net/connect-docs/create-a-proxy-configuration.html) documentation.

The transport layer in OpenVPN Access Server refers to the layer of the Open Systems Interconnection (OSI) model that is responsible for the reliable transmission of data between two endpoints. In the context of OpenVPN Access Server, the transport layer is responsible for establishing and maintaining the secure connection between the client and the server, ensuring the confidentiality, integrity, and authenticity of the data being transmitted.

To translate a video into written text using YouTube's automatic captions, you can follow these steps:

1. Open the video on YouTube.
2. Click on the "CC" button located at the bottom right corner of the video player. This will enable the automatic captions.
3. If the video already has captions available, you can click on the "Settings" icon next to the "CC" button and select the desired language for the captions.
4. If the video doesn't have captions available in your desired language, you can click on the "Settings" icon and select "Auto-translate." This will automatically translate the captions into your preferred language.
5. Once the captions are enabled and translated, you can view the written text by reading the captions displayed on the video.

Please note that the accuracy of automatic captions may vary depending on the quality of the audio and the language being spoken.

speaker: assistant
message:
Incident response and forensics are two important components of cybersecurity. 

Incident response refers to the process of detecting, responding to, and mitigating security incidents in an organization's IT environment. It involves identifying and containing the incident, investigating the cause and impact, and implementing measures to prevent future incidents. The goal of incident response is to minimize the damage caused by an incident and restore normal operations as quickly as possible.

Forensics, on the other hand, is the practice of collecting, analyzing, and preserving digital evidence related to a security incident. It involves using specialized techniques and tools to investigate the incident, identify the attacker, and gather evidence that can be used for legal proceedings if necessary. Forensics helps in understanding the scope and impact of the incident and provides valuable insights for improving security measures.

Both incident response and forensics play a crucial role in cybersecurity by helping organizations effectively respond to and recover from security incidents, as well as prevent future incidents.

message: What are some ways to find a therapist through referrals?

welcome_message:
Hello! I'm agent theraguide.
I'm here to answer any questions you have, or maybe you'd rather choose a question others are asking me?
[more about me >](action/profile)
speaker: assistant
message:
Referrals can be a great way to find a therapist. Here are some ways to find a therapist through referrals:

1. Ask your friends and family if they can recommend a therapist. They might have personal experiences and insights that can help you make a decision.

2. Reach out to your school's student health department or psychology department. They are likely well-connected with a network of qualified therapists.

3. Contact your insurance company. They can provide you with a list of psychotherapists they work with and whose services they cover.

4. Seek recommendations from other professionals you know and trust, even if they don't work in the healthcare field. Consider asking doctors, lawyers, and other professionals in your network.

5. If you're part of a religious community, people there may be able to offer recommendations.

Remember, even if a therapist works well for someone you know, they may not be the best fit for you. It's important to consider your personal needs and therapy goals when choosing a therapist.

message: What are some factors to consider when choosing a therapist?

welcome_message:
Hello! I'm agent theraguide.
I'm here to answer any questions you have, or maybe you'd rather choose a question others are asking me?
[more about me >](action/profile)
speaker: assistant
message:
When choosing a therapist, there are several factors to consider:

1. **Type of therapy**: Choose a type of therapy that aligns with your goals, such as cognitive behavioral therapy (CBT), acceptance and commitment therapy (ACT), dialectical behavior therapy (DBT), or psychoanalytic therapy.

2. **Cost**: Consider the cost of therapy and whether it fits within your budget. Some therapy options may be available for free or at a lower cost, while others may be more expensive.

3. **Referrals**: Ask for recommendations from friends, family, or professionals in your network. They may have insights or connections to qualified therapists.

4. **Credentials**: Check the therapist's credentials to ensure they are licensed to practice in your area. Additionally, consider their specific expertise or specialization in the type of therapy you're interested in.

5. **Cultural or community fit**: Some people find it easier to open up to therapists who understand their experiences. Consider factors such as gender identity, racial or cultural background, specialization in LGBTQIA+ issues, or religious affiliations.

6. **Therapy goals**: Determine what you want to focus on in therapy, whether it's dealing with stress, trauma, phobias, relationships, grief, mental health conditions, or emotional issues. Communicate your goals to potential therapists.

7. **Questions to ask**: Inquire about the therapist's areas of expertise, type of therapy practiced, experience with similar situations, approach, and years of practice. Also, ask about fees and insurance coverage.

Remember, finding the right therapist may involve some trial and error, but it's worth the effort to establish a beneficial working relationship.

7. Save your script for later or record your video while simultaneously reading the script from the teleprompter.

Congratulations! You've created your script for the job interview gameshow where the contestants are confused. Have fun recording your video! 🥳

message: What are the top must-know features?

welcome_message:
Hi! I'm BIGVU's AI support bot. 
How can I help you today?
speaker: assistant
message:
BIGVU offers several AI-powered tools to enhance your video creation process. Here are some of the must-know features provided by BIGVU:

1. AI Script Generator: BIGVU helps you create scripts 10x faster by generating multiple script options based on your business and talking points.

2. Teleprompter: BIGVU's teleprompter feature lets you view your script while recording, helping you speak confidently on camera. You can customize the speed and font size to match your natural pace.

3. Auto Captions: BIGVU automatically generates captions for your videos, making it easier for viewers to follow along. You can also use AI to highlight important words or phrases in the captions.

4. Video Styling: BIGVU provides editing tools to style and brand your videos. You can add backgrounds, music, picture overlays, cropping, and titling to give your videos a polished look.

5. AI Eye Contact: If you looked away from the camera during your recording, you can use BIGVU AI instead of retaking the video. The AI Eye Contact will make it appear like you are looking directly at your audience.

6. Social Media Scheduling: With one tap, you can schedule and post your video across all your social media channels.

These features make BIGVU a powerful tool for creating professional and engaging videos.

message:
If you're experiencing issues with audio recording in the BIGVU app, there could be a few possible reasons. Here are some troubleshooting steps you can try:

1. Make sure that your device's microphone is not muted or blocked. Check your device's settings to ensure that the microphone is enabled for the BIGVU app.

2. Check if the app has permission to access your device's microphone. You can do this by going to your device's settings, finding the BIGVU app, and making sure that microphone permissions are granted.

3. Ensure that you have a stable internet connection. Poor internet connectivity can sometimes affect audio recording in the app.

4. Try restarting the app or your device. Sometimes, a simple restart can resolve temporary glitches or conflicts that may be causing the audio recording issue.

If none of these steps resolve the problem, it's recommended to reach out to BIGVU support for further assistance. You can chat with them or email [support@bigvu.tv](mailto:support@bigvu.tv) for help with your specific issue.

welcome_message:
Hi! I'm BIGVU's AI support bot. 
How can I help you today?
speaker: assistant
message:
To delete your BIGVU account permanently and stop receiving notifications, you can follow these steps:

1. **Web Platform:**
   - Click on your Profile Picture in the top-right corner to access your profile page.
   - On the left-hand menu, click "Preferences."
   - Scroll down to the "Data and Privacy" section.
   - Choose "Delete Account."
   - Enter your email address in the pop-up box and click "Delete."

2. **Mobile App (Android & iOS):**
   - Click on the Profile Icon on the right of the bottom menu.
   - Tap on "My Subscription."
   - Scroll down and select "Delete Account."
   - Enter your email address and click on "Delete BIGVU Account."

Please note that deleting your account will permanently remove your video projects, scripts, media assets, and videos. Additionally, deleting the BIGVU app from your device does not delete your account or cancel your subscription. If you have any further questions or need assistance, you can reach out to [support@bigvu.tv](mailto:support@bigvu.tv).

speaker: assistant
message:
If you've created a video but the captions are not appearing, there could be a few reasons for this. 

First, make sure that you have added automatic captions to your video. You can do this by opening the Video Maker and selecting the option to add automatic captions. 

If you have already added automatic captions and they are still not appearing, you may need to manually edit and highlight the captions. In the Video Maker, you can edit the captions on each segment and highlight specific parts of the caption. To do this, right-click or double-click on the selected word you want to highlight and choose either "Highlight" or "Extra Highlight" to apply the desired highlighting. 

Once you have finished editing and highlighting the captions, remember to save your video by clicking the Create button. This will ensure that the captions are included in the final version of your video. 

If you're still experiencing issues with captions not appearing, please let us know and we'll be happy to assist you further.

message:
To cancel your BIGVU subscription, you can follow these steps based on the platform you used to create your account:

Please note that canceling your subscription will revert your plan to a free account, and your videos will be stored locally.

4. Check that you are using the same email address as the one you used to log in to the BIGVU Desk.

By using the same account on both the desktop and the app, you will be able to link them together and access your content seamlessly.

message: How do I use the script

welcome_message:
Hi! I'm BIGVU's AI support bot. 
How can I help you today?
speaker: assistant
message:
To use the BIGVU script, you have two options: AI script or from scratch.

For AI script:
1. In the mobile app, click on the "+" button in the center of the bottom menu and choose "AI Magic Writer".
2. Enter the title of your script and click on the "AI Rewrite Button" to access the AI Magic Writer.
3. Choose the type of script you want to create from the options available.
4. Follow the prompts and enter the necessary information.
5. Once the script is generated, you can edit it if needed.

For a script from scratch:
1. On the web platform, click on the "New Script" button on the Projects page.
2. Enter the title of your script.
3. Choose the type of script you want to create.
4. Enter the required information for the script.
5. Click "Write new" to generate your script.

After creating your script, you can choose to read and record it from the teleprompter, practice reading it without recording, or even live stream while reading it.

1. Log in to the account that you want to keep as the main account.
2. Go to the "Add Member" option in the left-hand menu.
3. Choose "Invite Member" and enter the email address of the other account.
4. Select the role you want the other account to have.
5. Click "Invite" to send the invitation to the other account.
6. Once the invitation is accepted, the other account will be added as a member to your main account.
7. You can now manage both accounts from the main account, including assigning tasks and controlling permission levels.

Please note that a member can only be added to a team account if they are not an existing BIGVU user. If the other account is already associated with a BIGVU user, you may need to use a different email address or contact support for further assistance.

speaker: assistant
message:
To delete your BIGVU account, follow these steps:

1. **Web Platform:**
   - Click on your Profile Picture in the top-right corner to access your profile page.
   - On the left-hand menu, click "Preferences."
   - Scroll down to the "Data and Privacy" section.
   - Choose "Delete Account."
   - Enter your email address in the pop-up box and click "Delete."

2. **Mobile App (Android & iOS):**
   - Click on the Profile Icon on the right of the bottom menu.
   - Tap on "My Subscription."
   - Scroll down and select "Delete Account."
   - Enter your email address and click on "Delete BIGVU Account."

Please note that once your account is deleted, it is impossible to recover your video projects, including scripts, media assets, and videos. It is recommended to export all your videos and scripts from the BIGVU desk before deleting your account. You can find more information on how to export your data from BIGVU in the [How do I export my data from BIGVU?](https://faq.bigvu.tv/en/articles/8075971-export-all-scripts-and-video-projects) article.

If you need further assistance, you can reach out to BIGVU support at [support@bigvu.tv](mailto:support@bigvu.tv).

message:
To upload a video from your iPad to your MacBook Pro, you can follow these steps:

1. Open the relevant video project on your iPad.
2. Check if the video is already uploaded to the cloud by looking for a "cloud icon" on the top right of the video thumbnail. If it's not uploaded, proceed to the next step.
3. Select the local take of the video on your iPad.
4. On the top right of the video screen, click on the three-dot menu.
5. From the menu, select "Upload to web app" to upload the video to the BIGVU Cloud.
6. Once the video is uploaded to the cloud, you can access it from your MacBook Pro by logging into the BIGVU web app using the same email and password.
7. Your video will be available in the web app, and you can download it to your MacBook Pro from there.

Please note that this process requires an internet connection and a BIGVU subscription.

1. Make sure you have a stable internet connection: Check that you are connected to a reliable Wi-Fi network or have a strong mobile data signal.

2. Clear cache and cookies: If you're accessing the app through a web browser, clearing your browser's cache and cookies can help resolve any loading or formatting issues. 3. Check camera permissions: If you're using the web platform, ensure that your browser has permission to access your camera. On iOS, go to System Preferences > Security and Privacy > enable camera permissions for Chrome. On Windows/Chrome, clear your browser's cache and relaunch it.

4. Update the app: If you're using the mobile app, make sure you have the latest version installed. Check for any available updates in your device's app store.

If these steps don't resolve the issue, please reach out to BIGVU support for further assistance.

3. **BIGVU Website:** Login to your account on the BIGVU website at [desk.bigvu.tv](https://desk.bigvu.tv/). Click on the profile icon in the top right corner, then select "Billing" from the dropdown menu. In the billing screen, choose "cancel subscription."

Please note that canceling your subscription will revert your plan to a free account, and your videos will be stored locally.

1. Open the relevant video in the project screen.

3. In the Take Screen, select the desired take by clicking the three-dot menu beneath its name.

6. You can also add your own intro/outro video by clicking "Upload Video" and selecting the video from your device.
7. Once you're satisfied with the changes, click the "Create" button on the top right side of the page to save your video.

If you need more help, you can refer to the [documentation](https://faq.bigvu.tv/en/articles/6386139-add-intro-outro-to-your-video-web) for detailed instructions.

message: What are the two forms of lighting in Unity?

welcome_message:
Hello! I'm agent academia-android.
I'm here to answer any questions you have, or maybe you'd rather choose a question others are asking me?
speaker: assistant
message: Unity offers two forms of lighting: real-time lighting and pre-rendered lighting. Real-time lighting recalculates the lighting constantly to maintain coherence in the scene when objects or lights move. It can be computationally expensive and may cause performance issues, especially on mobile devices. Pre-rendered lighting, on the other hand, provides higher quality lighting and is recommended for static scenes. It involves pre-rendering the lighting with shadows for each object in the scene.

1. Choose the Right Tools: Select and set up the right analytics suite that will provide you with the insights you need. This can include tools like Google Analytics and specialized local SEO tools.

4. Interpret and Act on the Data: Analyze the data from your dashboard to identify trends, opportunities, and areas for improvement. Use these insights to make strategic adjustments to your local SEO strategy, such as optimizing your Google My Business listing or refining your content strategy for local search.

5. Regular Reporting: Regularly report on your local SEO performance to track progress and communicate the value of your efforts to stakeholders. This will help you stay informed and adapt quickly to changes in the local SEO landscape.

Remember, creating a valuable and user-friendly online presence is key to succeeding in local SEO. By monitoring and optimizing your performance through a custom dashboard, you can position your business for online success.

message: What are the costs associated with operating a printing business?

welcome_message:
Hello! I'm agent note-3656.
I'm here to answer any questions you have, or maybe you'd rather choose a question others are asking me?
speaker: assistant
message:
The costs associated with operating a printing business include:

1. Equipment Costs: Printers, copiers, binding machines, laminators, and other equipment.
2. Supplies: Paper, ink, toner, chemicals, and other consumables.
3. Rent and Utilities: Cost of the physical space, electricity, water, heating, and cooling.
4. Labor: Wages for employees, including operators, designers, management, janitorial, and administrative staff.
5. Maintenance and Repairs: Regular maintenance and occasional repairs for equipment.
6. Marketing and Advertising: Promotional materials, advertising campaigns, and online marketing costs.
7. Insurance: Liability insurance, property insurance, and possibly health insurance for employees.
8. Software: Design software, MIS software, accounting software, and other business tools.
9. Taxes: Business taxes, sales tax, and possibly payroll taxes.
10. Shipping and Delivery: Cost of delivering finished products to customers.
11. Professional Services: Accounting, legal, and possibly consulting services.

Please note that this is not an exhaustive list, and the specific costs may vary depending on the size and scope of the printing business.

message: How does a predictive dialer work?

welcome_message:
Hello! I'm agent aircall-support.
I'm here to answer any questions you have, or maybe you'd rather choose a question others are asking me?
speaker: assistant
message:
A predictive dialer is a type of dialer that calls multiple numbers simultaneously and uses machine learning to maximize efficiency. Here's how it works:

1. The predictive dialer system starts by dialing multiple phone numbers at the same time. It uses an algorithm to determine the optimal number of calls to make based on factors like the number of available agents and the average rate of call connections.

2. As the calls are being made, the predictive dialer system analyzes the call data in real-time. It studies factors such as pauses, opening phrases, and other conversation traits to predict the likelihood of a call being answered by a live person.

3. Based on the analysis, the predictive dialer system determines which calls are likely to be answered by a live person and which calls are likely to result in voicemails or no answers. It then assigns the live calls to available sales representatives.

4. The predictive dialer system continues to monitor and adjust its calling strategy based on the ongoing call data. It learns from previous calls and adapts its dialing patterns to increase the chances of connecting with prospects.

5. When a sales representative finishes a call, the predictive dialer system automatically dials the next number in the queue, ensuring a continuous flow of calls without any manual intervention.

The goal of a predictive dialer is to maximize the efficiency of sales representatives by minimizing idle time and connecting them with live prospects. By dialing multiple numbers simultaneously and using machine learning to predict call connections, a predictive dialer helps sales teams reach more prospects in less time.

message: How can I integrate Aircall with Zendesk?

welcome_message:
Hello! I'm agent aircall-support.
I'm here to answer any questions you have, or maybe you'd rather choose a question others are asking me?
speaker: assistant
message:
To integrate Aircall with Zendesk, you can follow these steps:

1. Go to the Zendesk App Marketplace and search for the Aircall integration.
2. Click on the Aircall integration and select "Install" to add it to your Zendesk account.
3. Once installed, go to your Aircall dashboard and navigate to the Integrations section.
4. Find the Zendesk integration and click on "Configure" to set it up.
5. You will be prompted to enter your Zendesk subdomain and API token. Follow the instructions to generate an API token in Zendesk if you don't have one already.
6. After entering the required information, click on "Connect" to establish the integration between Aircall and Zendesk.
7. Once the integration is set up, you can start making and receiving calls directly from the Zendesk interface. Incoming calls will be matched to existing customer records, and you can create tickets automatically.
8. You can also access call information, including numbers, dates, times, recordings, and voicemails, in dedicated Zendesk custom fields.
9. Use this information to improve customer service, automate workflows, and generate reports in Zendesk Explore.

Please note that these steps are a general guideline, and the specific process may vary slightly depending on the versions and configurations of Aircall and Zendesk. For more detailed instructions and troubleshooting, you can refer to the official Aircall documentation on integrating with Zendesk.

To integrate Aircall with HubSpot, you can follow these steps:

1. Log in to your Aircall Dashboard.
2. Select "Integrations & API" located in the navigation menu on the left-hand side.
3. Under the "Integrations" section, click on "HubSpot."
4. Click on "Install Integration" to authorize the integration.
5. Follow the prompts to connect your Aircall account with HubSpot.
6. Once the integration is set up, you'll be able to make and receive phone calls directly from your Aircall app within HubSpot.

For more detailed instructions and information, you can refer to the [HubSpot integration documentation](https://developer.aircall.io/call-center-software-integrations/reamaze/).

message: How do I use the script

welcome_message:
Hi! I'm BIGVU's AI support bot. 
How can I help you today?
speaker: assistant
message:
To use the BIGVU script, you have two options: AI script or from scratch.

For AI script:
1. In the mobile app, click on the "+" button in the center of the bottom menu and choose "AI Magic Writer".
2. Enter the title of your script and click on the "AI Rewrite Button" to access the AI Magic Writer.
3. Choose the type of script you want to create from the options available.
4. Follow the prompts and enter the necessary information.
5. Once the script is generated, you can edit it if needed.

For creating a script from scratch:
1. On the web platform, click on the "New Script" button on the Projects page.
2. Enter the title of your script.
3. Choose the type of script you want to create.
4. Enter the required information for the script.
5. Click "Write new" to generate your script.

After creating your script, you can choose to edit it or send it to the teleprompter to start recording.

message: How do I delete my account

welcome_message:
Hi! I'm BIGVU's AI support bot. 
How can I help you today?
speaker: assistant
message:
To delete your BIGVU account, follow these steps:

1. **Web Platform:**
   - Click on your Profile Picture in the top-right corner to access your profile page.
   - On the left-hand menu, click "Preferences."
   - Scroll down to the "Data and Privacy" section.
   - Choose "Delete Account."
   - Enter your email address in the pop-up box and click "Delete."

2. **Mobile App (Android & iOS):**
   - Click on the Profile Icon on the right of the bottom menu.
   - Tap on "My Subscription."
   - Scroll down and select "Delete Account."
   - Enter your email address and click on "Delete BIGVU Account."

Please note that deleting your account will permanently remove all your video projects, scripts, media assets, and videos. Make sure to export all your data before deleting your account. If you need further assistance, you can reach out to [support@bigvu.tv](mailto:support@bigvu.tv).

welcome_message:
Hi! I'm BIGVU's AI support bot. 
How can I help you today?
speaker: assistant
message:
If you're experiencing issues with recording and uploading a video on BIGVU from your laptop, there could be a few reasons for this. Here are some troubleshooting steps you can try:

1. Check your internet connection: Make sure you have a stable internet connection before recording or uploading a video. A weak or unstable connection can cause issues with the recording process.

2. Clear your browser cache: Clearing your browser cache can help resolve any temporary issues that may be causing the screen to freeze or not respond. You can usually find this option in your browser's settings.

3. Try a different browser: If you're using a specific browser and experiencing issues, try using a different browser to see if the problem persists. Sometimes, certain browsers may have compatibility issues with certain websites or applications.

4. Update your browser: Make sure you're using the latest version of your browser. Outdated versions may not be fully compatible with BIGVU and can cause issues with recording and uploading videos.

If none of these steps resolve the issue, it's recommended to reach out to BIGVU support for further assistance. They will be able to provide more specific guidance based on your situation.

4. In the web app, you will be able to find the uploaded video take in your project and continue working with it on your MacBook Pro.

Please note that this process requires an internet connection and a BIGVU subscription.

welcome_message:

message:
Adding music and titles to your videos can be done on both desktop and mobile devices. If you have upgraded your plan, you should have access to these features. Here's how you can add music and titles on desktop:

1. Open the relevant video you want to edit on the project screen.
2. Click on the three dots menu and choose "Edit" to open the Take Screen.
3. In the Take Screen, click on the three dots menu below the desired take and choose "Open Video Maker" to stylize your video.
4. In the Video Maker, go to the Style button on the left sidebar.
5. Under the "Music" section, choose a music track to add to your video.
6. To add titles, go to the "Text" section in the left sidebar and click on the "Add Text" button.
7. Enter your desired text and customize the font, size, color, and position of the title.
8. Once you're done, click on the "Save" button to apply the changes to your video.

Please note that it may take a few minutes for your changes to update. If you're not seeing the option to add music and titles, try refreshing the page or clearing your browser cache.

speaker: assistant
message:
If you're experiencing issues with the saved video not displaying correctly after recording on your Android phone, it could be due to the screen refresh rate of your device. Newer Android devices with a 120 Hz refresh rate may cause compatibility issues with the app. To resolve this, you can try adjusting the screen refresh rate to 60 Hz. Here's how:

1. Go to your device settings.
2. Search for and select "Motion smoothness."
3. Tap "Motion smoothness" again and choose "Standard refresh rate - 60 Hz refresh rate."

This should help resolve the issue with the saved video not displaying correctly. Keep in mind that BIGVU will soon support 120 Hz refresh rate as well.

message:

     - Click on the 3 dots menu of the Video Maker Project.
     - Select Download.
     - Choose the type of file you wish to download: MP4 or WebM.

That's it! You can now download your video file from BIGVU.

7. When you're finished recording, stop the teleprompter and review your video.
8. Edit your video if needed, and then save or share it.

That's it! You can now create videos using a teleprompter on your laptop with BIGVU Teleprompter.

speaker: assistant
message:
Is your camera not connecting when you start recording with the teleprompter? Are you seeing the "spinning wheel of death" in your camera box? The camera might appear as an option, but this doesn't mean the permissions are enabled for Chrome on your device. Sometimes, when your operating system updates, the camera permissions for Chrome can change without warning. 

For iOs Web, you can grant camera permissions by clicking on the apple logo on the top left of your screen, choosing "System preferences", selecting Security and Privacy, and enabling camera permissions for Chrome by ticking the checkbox beside it.

For Windows/Chrome Web, you can clear your browser's cache to reset your camera's permission request. Open your Chrome browser, click the 3 dots at the upper right corner of the browser's window, select Settings, go to Privacy and Security, then click on Clear browsing data. Set the time range to "All time" and clear cookies and other site data, as well as cached images and files. Once done, close all your browsers, then relaunch it and try to record again.

If you need further assistance, you can send a message to [support@bigvu.tv](mailto:support@bigvu.tv).

welcome_message:

speaker: assistant
message:
To upload a video to BIGVU, you have a few options:

1) If you have just recorded a video using the BIGVU web platform or mobile app, your video will be automatically saved and available on both the web platform and mobile app. You can download it in either .webm or .mp4 format.

2) If you didn't upload your video directly after recording, you can still upload it to the cloud. Go to the Project screen, click on the 3 dots next to your project, and select "Edit". Then, in the Take screen, click on the 3 dots under your take and select "Upload" to find your video in all your platforms.

Please note that uploading to the cloud may take a few minutes and should be done using a stable and strong WiFi connection. Make sure you have enough memory space on your device and that your device's time and date are set to automatic.

3. Double-check that the captions are enabled in the settings of your video player. Sometimes, captions may be disabled by default, so you need to enable them to see the captions.

This should help resolve the issue with the saved video not displaying correctly. Keep in mind that BIGVU will soon support 120 Hz refresh rate as well.

Sometimes, when your operating system updates, the camera permissions for Chrome can change without warning.

For Windows/Chrome Web, you can clear your browser's cache to reset your camera's permission request. Open your Chrome browser, click the 3 dots at the upper right corner of the browser's window, select Settings, go to Privacy and Security, then click on Clear browsing data. Set the time range to "All time" and clear cookies and other site data, as well as cached images and files. Once done, close all your browsers, then relaunch it and try to record again.

message: Hello, I just upgraded my subscription to Starter. I created a video under Projects and want to add an intro and outro. However, when I click on the three dots to the right of my name, the only options I have are Edit, Duplicate, and Delete. How do I get the other options?

welcome_message:
Hi! I'm BIGVU's AI support bot. 
How can I help you today?
speaker: assistant
message:
To add an intro and outro to your video in BIGVU, follow these steps:

1. Open the relevant video in the project screen.
2. Click on the three dots menu and choose "Edit" for the video you want to add the intro and outro to.
3. In the Take Screen, select the desired take by clicking the three-dot menu beneath its name.
4. A pop-up window will appear, offering you the option to choose "Open Video Maker" to stylize your video.
5. In the Video Maker, go to the Style button on the left sidebar and choose an intro or an outro.
6. You can also add your own intro/outro video by clicking "Upload Video" and selecting the video from your device.
7. Once you're satisfied with the changes, click the "Create" button on the top right side of the page to save your video.

For more detailed instructions, you can refer to the [documentation](https://faq.bigvu.tv/en/articles/6386139-add-intro-outro-to-your-video-web).

BIGVU offers several AI-powered tools to enhance your video creation process. Here are some of the must-know features provided by BIGVU:

1. AI Script Generator: BIGVU helps you create scripts 10x faster by generating multiple script options based on your business and talking points.

2. Teleprompter: BIGVU's teleprompter feature lets you view your script while recording, helping you speak confidently on camera. You can customize the speed and font size to match your natural pace.

3. Auto Captions: BIGVU automatically generates captions for your videos, making it easier for viewers to follow along. You can also use AI to highlight important words or phrases in the captions.

4. Video Styling: BIGVU provides editing tools to style and brand your videos. You can add backgrounds, music, picture overlays, cropping, and titling to give your videos a polished look.

5. AI Eye Contact: If you looked away from the camera during your recording, you can use BIGVU AI instead of retaking the video. The AI Eye Contact will make it appear like you are looking directly at your audience.

6. Social Media Scheduling: With one tap, you can schedule and post your video across all your social media channels.

These features make BIGVU a powerful tool for creating professional and engaging videos.

2- How to analyze the truthfulness of information received from social media?

welcome_message:
Hello! I'm agent hasan.
I'm here to answer any questions you have, or maybe you'd rather choose a question others are asking me?
speaker: assistant
message:
1- Empiricism and Rationalism are two contrasting theories in epistemology. Empiricism posits that knowledge comes primarily from sensory experience. It emphasizes the importance of observation, experimentation, and evidence-based reasoning. According to empiricists, the truth of a scientific claim is determined by its empirical verification. For example, in the field of medicine, empirical evidence from clinical trials and experiments is used to assess the effectiveness of a new drug.

On the other hand, Rationalism asserts that the rational mind is the primary source of knowledge. It emphasizes the role of reason, logic, and innate ideas. Rationalists believe that certain truths can be known through pure reason, independent of sensory experience. An example of rationalism in assessing the truth of a scientific claim is the use of mathematical proofs in physics to establish fundamental laws and principles.

These two theories can lead to different approaches in assessing the truth of a scientific claim. Empiricism relies on empirical evidence and experimentation to validate scientific claims, while Rationalism relies on logical reasoning and deductive arguments. Empiricism emphasizes the importance of observation and data collection, while Rationalism emphasizes the role of reason and logical coherence.

2- Analyzing the truthfulness of information received from social media requires critical thinking and evaluation. Here are some steps to assess the truthfulness of information:

1. Source credibility: Consider the credibility and expertise of the source sharing the information. Look for reputable sources, such as established news organizations or experts in the field.

2. Fact-checking: Verify the information by cross-referencing it with other reliable sources. Fact-checking websites can help identify misinformation or false claims.

3. Bias and perspective: Be aware of potential biases or agendas that may influence the information. Consider multiple perspectives and sources to get a more balanced view.

4. Evidence and supporting data: Look for evidence and supporting data that back up the claims being made. Evaluate the quality and reliability of the evidence presented.

5. Critical thinking: Apply critical thinking skills to analyze the logic and coherence of the information. Look for logical fallacies or inconsistencies in the argument.

By following these steps, one can make a more informed judgment about the truthfulness of information received from social media.

message: When it comes to veganism, there are a few key points to consider. First, veganism is not solely about health but also encompasses ethical and environmental concerns. While veganism can be a healthy way to eat, it's important to note that a poorly planned vegan diet can lead to nutritional deficiencies. Vegans may need to pay attention to getting enough calcium, iron, omega-3 fatty acids, vitamin D, and vitamin B12, as these nutrients are commonly found in animal-based foods. Additionally, B12 is almost completely absent from plant-based foods. It's crucial for vegans to ensure they have a well-rounded and balanced diet to meet their nutritional needs.

message:
Vegans can eat a variety of foods, including:

- Fruits
- Vegetables
- Legumes
- Nondairy milk, yogurt, cheese, ice cream, etc.
- Whole grains
- Nuts and seeds
- Soy products (tempeh, tofu, edamame, soymilk)
- Non-egg-based pasta
- Non-egg-based bread
- Herbs and spices
- Yeast and nutritional yeast

It's important to note that every vegan may have different guidelines and standards, so it's always a good idea to double-check the ingredients in packaged goods and look for vegan labels and certifications on food packages.

message:
According to the documentation, vegans can eat a variety of foods, including:

- Fruits
- Vegetables
- Legumes
- Nondairy milk, yogurt, cheese, ice cream, etc.
- Whole grains
- Nuts and seeds
- Soy products (tempeh, tofu, edamame, soymilk)
- Non-egg-based pasta
- Non-egg-based bread
- Herbs and spices
- Yeast and nutritional yeast

However, vegans should avoid eating:

- Meat and poultry
- Seafood
- Eggs
- Butter, milk, yogurt, cheese, ice cream
- Egg-based pasta
- Egg-based breads
- Honey
- Whey
- Gelatin
- Lactose
- Casein

It's important to note that individual vegans may have different guidelines and standards, and some foods may be made with animal byproducts during processing. It's always a good idea to double-check the ingredients in packaged goods and look for vegan labels and certifications.

It is associated with various characteristics such as electricity, computers, flight, democracy, freedom, humanitarianism, idealism, and rebellion. The exact start date of the Age of Aquarius is a topic of debate among astrologers.

6. **Implement Pricing Strategies**: Explore different pricing strategies to maximize your rental income. Research the prices of other rentals in your area and set competitive rates.

7. **Promote Your Listing**: Develop marketing strategies to promote your Airbnb listing. Utilize social media, online platforms, and other marketing channels to reach potential guests.

To manually install the OpenVPN Access Server, you can download the necessary package installer files and install them on your Linux system. Here are the steps:

1. Log in to your Linux system either on the console or via SSH with root privileges.
